name: Cube Dodger (isaacyoshimario)
description:
It's Cube Dodger.

You are a green cube. You are trying to avoid the red and blue cubes. The small green ones are your friends.

5 Difficulties.

Catchy songs.

Lots of fun.

(message to itch) Please take this game down if you need to, I might have made some copyright issue with the music. Contact me if this is really serious.
